name: Andy's Cat
description: In the wild world of "Boys Club," where degens and stoners kick it, Andy was always vibing with his chaotic crew, including the infamous Pepe. But Andy wasn't just about that chill life; he had a lowkey secret that's just gone viral thanks to a wild new mission: his cat, Candy. Yeah, so here’s the scoop—Andy's secret about Candy has just blasted into the spotlight because now, they're both on a mission to the freaking moon!
